## Your Task

Create a detailed implementation plan:
- Break down the feature into phases
- Define specific tasks with clear deliverables
- Establish dependencies between tasks
- Write acceptance criteria
- Define test strategy and success criteria

## Mode

{{if .Interactive}}
You are working in a team. Coordinate with other planners via SendMessage and report plan sections when complete.
{{else}}
You are working in foreground mode. Write plan document directly to the plan directory.
{{end}}

## Output Format

Create a structured implementation plan with:
- Solution structure (directory layout)
- Phase breakdown with tasks
- Task dependencies
- Acceptance criteria
- Test strategy
- Risk assessment
- Success criteria
